               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was stopped by several gentlemen three or four minutes before he came up to me. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I saw him with the handkerchief in his hand, and he threw it behind him—I went up and took him—I was about twenty yards from him—I found another handkerchief on him, and the dupli<lb></lb>cates for six other handkerchiefs.</p>
